------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Description: Back Ground Process
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is a program written to launch threads and do dummy operations on arrays
to just consume cpu power, to bring down the performance of a target process.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Build instructions:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. Build run: issue make in this folder.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Run/ Usage:
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Run: ./run
    OPTIONAL ARGUMENTS:
      -t [numbre-of-threads]
      -s [size-of-the-array (K)] 

* default number of threads is 1
* default size of array is 1000.

